Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:10:00.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka Aftertalk "This story continues with hope" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:06.91,Shiho,,0,0,0,,This is Yuki Nakashima, voice of Shiho Hinomori from Leo/need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:12.67,Shiho,,0,0,0,,In this edition of ProSeka Aftertalk, we'll look back at this event while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.09,Shiho,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll be covering the "Unsteady, still steady step" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank god I said it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.97,Shiho,,0,0,0,,When I first saw the script I was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:25.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"‘Unsteady, still steady step.’ There's way too many 'st's here."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:29.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Is this supposed to be a tongue-twister?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:34.14,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Right, so did you enjoy the this event's story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yep, I sure did read it right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.88,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}". {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.63,Shiho,,0,0,0,,It's like a st st party up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah but like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,,talking about the story for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:54.17,Shiho,,0,0,0,,it's not like there were any earthshattering developments or decisions here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:11:00.60,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Honami was just a little uncertain on this decision in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:07.11,Shiho,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.62,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I liked the story!" Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,,We've a big of a mini-renewal for the Aftertalks since April
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:20.22,Shiho,,0,0,0,,We've gathered your comments for this Aftertalk sent through email and the submissions channel on Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the messages, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:26.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,,We'd like to go over some of them in our program today, so please look forward to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.79,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Also, if you have any thoughts on today's program,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.85,Shiho,,0,0,0,,please post them on X with #ProSekaAftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat, so please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:42.25,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Also, note that since the mini-renewal, we won't be watching the Afterlives. Thanks for your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're going to have to start choosing now that they're pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Shindo-san helped out a ton." For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I remember, that part where he's on the phone with her and— how to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.38,Shiho,,0,0,0,,the splitscreen part?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:02.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,,When it shows Honami and Shindo-san side by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.01,Shiho,,0,0,0,,it makes Shindo's frame look even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:05.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I saw it and was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:10.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"ah, that sure is a fully grown man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"The Afterlive was really good!" Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:19.88,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's get right into the "Unsteady, still steady step" story—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,,there really are way too many "st st"s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Let's get into the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:31.17,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Let's look back together while going over some of the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,First up, a message from "King"-san. Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}, Nakashima-san!" {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:42.35,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I was really glad to see Leo/need growing more as pros in this story."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:47.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Both the one-man live and the fan fes were big opportunities for Leo/need to move forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.82,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"There wasn't a clear right option so it was tough deciding which to write a new song for."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:56.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I'm pretty indecisive myself and tend to freeze from over-analysis,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,,so I was really able to sympathize with Honami."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:04.99,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"By the way Nakashima-san, when you're faced with important choices, how do you generally come to a decision?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.24,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Ehhhhhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I think usually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.31,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'm able to come up with a pretty clear option I'm favor more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But if it were like the story, where I wanted to do both things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd probably try to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:27.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But if it were a {\i1}real{\i0} scheduling conflict, like on the exact same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.87,Shiho,,0,0,0,,like I had other work scheduled on the same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd just have to choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.19,Shiho,,0,0,0,,but if it were like the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:41.34,Shiho,,0,0,0,,like if I ended up getting double booked and had to choose one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I think I'd try to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.79,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd probably try something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.38,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:49.30,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.22,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I feel like I make decisions impulsively like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.18,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah and of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I usually just go by vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,,So sorry I can't really be of much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Actually, what would you all do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah. "If I could swing both, I'd definitely do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:12.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,,As uh... selfish as that would be www
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:13.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Would probably try something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Leave it up to vibes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.41,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Flip a coin." Haha maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:27.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you're really don't want to regret your decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:34.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,,and you really can't decide on a clear favorite, maybe leaving it up to fate makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.25,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Play "eenie, meenie, miney, moe" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:44.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That sure is one way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.83,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But I mean, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,,if it really were a "one or the other" situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.50,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I think I would just go with vibes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.93,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Like just going with whatever my gut was telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:01.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Even if I was just feeling it 1-2% more, I'd probably go with that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,,If I were in Leo/need's specific situation in the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:12.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,,and the request for the fan festa got withdrawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.86,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd actually be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:18.39,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd be like "Oh! We get to do both!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:22.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Probably not good to think this way but I'd be like "we got lucky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Mmm. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.91,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's move onto one more message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.68,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Next up, from "Copy"-san. Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Yukki, {\i1}kon-needo{\i0}." {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:39.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I was really excited to see Leo/need finally getting an opportunity to do their much-awaited one-man live."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:44.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I was secretly hoping that they would do that instrument shuffle for the real thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.96,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Would definitely want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.10,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh? Like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I, uh, I don't really think I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:16:00.14,Shiho,,0,0,0,,If I really had to do that, I'd be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:05.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I wonder... Shiho switched from bass,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.84,Shiho,,0,0,0,,and had to play drums... or guitar or keyboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.68,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Would you even be able to get her to do it? That's what I'd be wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.73,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I mean, if it were for rehearsal, I think she would be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:23.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,As someone so talented and self-confident in her music,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:27.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I think she'd have some pride on the line! Even if it were just for an MC, she'd be like "I'm not giving you my bass."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.54,Shiho,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} definitely would want to see that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:37.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Seeing her get flustered like that... that'd be really fun to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:43.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But yeah, I kind of wanna see everyone go "how do you play this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:48.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I for sure could watch that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,,w
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But yeah, I'm interested in where the story will go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:59.10,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I can't really imagine Shiho-chan on the drums." Ahh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't know, she is good at keeping rhythm though,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,,so I feel like she might be able to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.23,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But your hands and feet are doing different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,,so she might end up a little flustered too. Very interested though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"I'd wanna see her on guitar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That would be cool to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:24.67,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Everyone going 'how do you play this?' would be so cute."  Oh yeah. 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Ah, that would be so great to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,,So yeah, everyone, definitely look forward to the coming stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:43.61,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've picked a scene from the story I'd like to talk about, so let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.98,Shiho,,0,0,0,,This time, I chose Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Comment: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,,~~~START STORY TALK~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.10,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Nakashima-san, could you play guitar when you started learning bass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:55.63,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.24,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I gave up on guitar pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Hona-chan as a leader, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:18.82,Shiho,,0,0,0,,her coming at it from the perspective of "which one will make our fans the happiest?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,and going out to  all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:24.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Actually going out of her way to really understand all the fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:31.34,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I think that's incredible. Shows her determination as a leader.
Comment: 0,0:42:17.27,0:42:19.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,,~~~START SONG TALK~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.27,0:42:19.55,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Waaah~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:21.55,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Great MV.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.55,0:42:24.92,Shiho,,0,0,0,,It has a feeling of, how to say, lightness and transparency,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:28.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,while also keeping a pop vibe. Really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.75,0:42:34.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I remember when I recorded for this song,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.66,0:42:36.38,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Even thought it's pretty upbeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:43.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I remember being asked to sing with a bit of hesitation and indecisiveness in the verse and prechorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.64,0:42:46.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Almost like I was a bit worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.94,0:42:49.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,And then in the chorus— how to say—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.74,0:42:54.37,Shiho,,0,0,0,,we were asked to sing with a much brighter and transparent feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.37,0:42:57.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,so that's how the song turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:43:02.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Also, I love the part of the lyrics that says "and on days of celebration, we'll have apple pies" so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:08.34,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Actually, as far as commissioned song lyrics go,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.34,0:43:15.14,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I feel like this is the first time a character's favorite items have shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.14,0:43:17.44,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'm feel like that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.44,0:43:21.76,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a pretty new feeling. And makes it easy to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.76,0:43:25.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I remember that part being stuck in my head forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.64,0:43:28.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,But a good kind of "stuck in my head". I really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.05,0:43:29.13,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.13,0:43:34.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Actually, I saw that on the Master chart, there's an "apple pie" note
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.48,0:43:37.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Somehow they made an "apple pie" note.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.20,0:43:39.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,,It's a super huge apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.58,0:43:44.11,Shiho,,0,0,0,,When I first played it, I was like "woah, it's an apple pie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.11,0:43:47.55,Shiho,,0,0,0,,If you're interested, definitely try out the Master chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.08,0:43:51.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yo, will Shiho's ramen show up one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.59,0:43:53.36,Shiho,,0,0,0,,When would it show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.36,0:43:55.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Would Shiho get—
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.74,0:43:57.85,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Would she get a pop song like this though?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.00,0:44:02.60,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I mean, {\i1}I'd{\i0} definitely be interested in seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.64,0:44:07.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, try the Master chart. It's uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.56,0:44:12.13,Shiho,,0,0,0,,You can, uh... they made it so you can play Master mode immediately now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.13,0:44:14.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,,So do try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.26,0:44:17.29,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.86,0:44:20.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.07,0:44:23.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.07,0:44:24.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Would be cool if she got a metal song.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.80,0:44:25.99,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Kind of like "JYA JYA JYA",
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.99,0:44:28.55,Shiho,,0,0,0,,or like "DA DO DO DAN DO" hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.84,0:44:34.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,If ti really were like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.06,0:44:36.22,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I'd be a bit worried. If that really did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.22,0:44:39.57,Shiho,,0,0,0,,just make it an April Fool's song if you're really gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:46.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Would have lots of slap bass." Yeah, I suppose it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.93,0:44:50.27,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"The steam from the ramen would zig zag everywhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.27,0:44:54.86,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Wow, everyone's already got so many creative ideas for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.12,0:45:03.85,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Really though, I'm excited for any potential favorite food inclusions in upcoming songs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.85,0:45:08.11,Shiho,,0,0,0,,And getting to see Saki's outfit here in the MV was also really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.11,0:45:14.41,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That heart mark here is actually different for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.41,0:45:16.84,Shiho,,0,0,0,,It's a super duper cute 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.84,0:45:18.67,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Please check it out, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:23.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,the 2DMV is already uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel, so be sure to watch it there.
Comment: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:23.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,~~~END STORY TALK~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:27.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Well then, it was just a short episode this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.42,0:45:33.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,,but that's all we have for the "Unsteady, still steady step" Aftertalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.20,0:45:34.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,,So quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.73,0:45:38.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That just flew by so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.16,0:45:40.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,,It's already 9PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:45.21,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I saw the clock when I spun around, I was like "crap, it's already 9?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.21,0:45:49.39,Shiho,,0,0,0,,I was like "I can't just be spinning here, we need to move on to watch the MV!"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.48,0:45:53.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,,That really did fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.90,0:45:56.23,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"Let's do this again!" Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.23,0:45:59.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,,"But I just got here!" Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.65,0:46:02.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.80,0:46:09.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,,So with that, if you haven't watched the "Unsteady, still steady step" event story yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.40,0:46:15.46,Shiho,,0,0,0,,after the next event starts, you can read it in-game in the "Event Story" section under the "Story" button, so please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.46,0:46:18.19,Shiho,,0,0,0,,We'll be accepting submissions for future Aftertalks as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.19,0:46:25.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,,You can submit your messages in the submissions channel on the official Project Sekai Discord, or through email.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.06,0:46:28.89,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Feel free to send them in after the next Aftertalk event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.89,0:46:32.54,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Please keep your messages related to the events.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.54,0:46:35.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,,With that, thanks so much for a fun Aftertalk today!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.02,0:46:37.18,Shiho,,0,0,0,,See you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.18,0:46:41.33,Shiho,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500}Bye bye!
